name: Jack Frost meets Santa Claus
description:
Sterling Silver Red Tartan & Crystal Set

Stunning bracelet & drop earring set. Created using sterling silver wire, red tartan, crystal quartz & sparkly silver beads.

Very Now, very festive, very glam, very pretty!

I LOVE, LOVE, LOVE this set!!...So will you xx

name: Charmed I'm Sure
description:
A Sterling Silver Charm Bracelet with a "wee" Scottish twist!

Sterling silver wire was used to create the frame. I then selected some gemstones to make the individual charms. I made the tartan charm & centered it, then chose gems to compliment the colours & style.

3 stunning emeralds in different shades, a rock of citrine, moonstone, aquamarine, crystal quartz, lapis lazuli, peridot & freshwater pearls.
These stones all remind me of Scotland in different ways..some are rugged, others smooth & clear!
I added a celtic clasp, which gives it a very individual look.

There is a matching ring as seen in the photos.

name: A Very Celtic Christmas
description:
Sterling Silver Pendant & Earring Set.

I created this with Xmas in mind! I selected a tartan with a Christmas feel to it...reds, dark blue & forrest green. 

A frame within a frame, tartan surrounded by silver & woven with silver wire & a beautiful ivory freshwater pearl.

The matching earrings have a tartan beaded drop, with more pearls, ruby chips & satin silver beads.
All together creating something beautifully unique, with a richness & festive feel. This Would look stunning with that "wee" black dress! x

The pendant comes with a 22" chain. Other lengths available on request.

name: 3 Tiered Amethyst/Crystal Bracelet

This handcrafted design has 30 unique amethyst, and crystal cubes encased by 3 Sterling Silver hoops.
Very beautiful featuring 4 amazing crystal quartz charms which are cut with the finest clarity.
Stunning piece.

name: Celtic Twist
description:
A Handmade Celtic themed set, made from the finest quality silver & gemstones.

This set has been created using rough rose quartz nuggets, rubies, peridot & silver celtic links.

I created the charm pendant with Scotland in mind, and a "wee" twist!. The crystal heart contains Scottish Heather & spring water, and can be opened. So smell away & remember how "Bonny" Scotland is!! x

The pendant comes with a 24" Sterling Silver chain.

I was asked to make this set for a birthday gift. Using the ladys favourite colours I selected these gorgeous pale green amethysts; which I encased in a sterling silver herringbone weave. I matched in the blue sapphires to create a bit of drama.
This is a very special and elegant creation x

E-Cig Charm made with Sterling Silver beads, links and tartan. I selected freshwater pearls, rubies, peridot & sapphire chips to compliment the tartan.

This charm is very unique & has a Christmasy feel to it x

Go on treat yourself! x

name: Twinkly Nights
description:
Stunning Amethyst & Sterling Sliver set. This consists of a delicate long length crystal pendant paired with matching earrings.x

Purple Amethyst has been highly esteemed throughout the ages for its stunning beauty and legendary powers to stimulate, and soothe, the mind and emotions. It is a semi-precious stone in today’s classifications, but to the ancients it was a “Gem of Fire,” a Precious Stone worth, at times in history, as much as a Diamond.

Very pretty, Very girly xx

The hematite brings a bit of depth to this set, which sets it apart from traditional designs. I attached a sterling silver floral clasp for added elegance.


Stunning one of a kind piece x

Tiger’s eye is a gemstone that resembles eye of tiger, it is very well known for its mystical properties. These gemstones are said to be of part power of the earth and part power of the sun. x

name: Exclusive "Vision Spinner" Bejewelled E-Cig
description: Glam it up! I was asked to create something feminine & pretty for the ever popular e-cig. This is what I came up with Sterling Silver spiral cage adorned with 4 different quality gemstones. Red Garnets, Pink Tigers Eye, Amethyst & Crystal Quartz. Vision Spinner with gemstone encrusted case, coiled around the device. It feels extremely comfortable and tactile in the hand, allowing for easy access to the voltage wheel, button and 510 connector. Comes with a charger. If you want a tank, then we can supply assorted styles to order, such as CE4, Protank, etc. Just drop us a line with your requirements. Don't forget to visit Planet of the Vapes for all your vaping community needs!

If you want a tank, then we can supply assorted styles to order, such as CE4, Protank, etc. Just drop us a line with your requirements. Genuine Hematite and Agate are threaded onto Copper wire and coiled around the device.
